{"tid":1882561,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"台灣第一例武漢肺炎死亡個案","createTime":"2020-02-16T10:35:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-16T10:45:39.000Z","uid":265112,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"94cb806cae605078d3633e4552aaffbdc861f43c","tid":1882561,"uid":265112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:35:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200216/1639881.htm?fbclid=IwAR2hwU2eHJqL_JRZKXpltlBHs5CKjpMcqXYzoy_ty6Lia2jpAYOXKtgNylU&amp;from=fb_et_news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200216%2F1639881.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2hwU2eHJqL_JRZKXpltlBHs5CKjpMcqXYzoy_ty6Lia2jpAYOXKtgNylU%26from%3Dfb_et_news&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbmo8q5%2FbnpuKyKF%2Fs7IAglk%3D&h=6bd55257\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200216/1639881.htm?fbclid=IwAR2hwU2eHJqL_JRZKXpltlBHs5CKjpMcqXYzoy_ty6Lia2jpAYOXKtgNylU&amp;from=fb_et_news</a><br />\n<br />\n首例死亡！新冠肺炎新增2例本土個案 60歲患者不治<br />\n<br />\n記者趙于婷／台北報導<br />\n<br />\n中央流行疫情指揮中心今（16）日再宣布2例新冠肺炎本土（COVID-19）確診個案，分別為第19、20例，19例無出國旅遊史，也不是密切接觸者，在2/15日晚間因肺炎合併敗血症死亡。<br />\n<br />\n死亡個案為中部60餘歲男性，有B型肝炎及糖尿病病史，無出國旅遊史，亦非確診病例之已知密切接觸者。於1月27日出現咳嗽，2月3日因呼吸急促赴醫院就醫，診斷為肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n當日收治於負壓加護病房治療，個案已於2月15日晚間因肺炎合併敗血症死亡，其遺體經家屬同意，將依法定傳染病規定進行火化，並保留部分檢體以供進一步檢驗。第2例為第1例之50餘歲男性家人，於昨日進行採檢後確診，目前個案無症狀，收治於負壓隔離病房。"},{"pid":"fabb6545a426b9af8f381ef50b1ea25588fde63e","tid":1882561,"uid":194326,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:38:11.000Z","msg":"WARS咪仲易記<br />\nCOVID-19，濕鳩專家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6795775738db9dd60d0ab25110692504671e24e","tid":1882561,"uid":92188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:39:15.000Z","msg":"其實都幾易死<br />\n好多救極都出唔到院已經係死硬"},{"pid":"e7e02c6f1eeb03ba19ca7f66b905239410ba1d6c","tid":1882561,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:39:37.000Z","msg":"都係高齡"},{"pid":"f5dc3b3ca5dab822be2751caeff9415d7f84a2b4","tid":1882561,"uid":227650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:40:32.000Z","msg":"又係有糖尿病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />香港嗰個都係"},{"pid":"8d382b537584cf6a5f6dec4c83c985f2d806a8af","tid":1882561,"uid":39855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"香港死果個又係有糖尿病，睇嚟 糖尿病 + 武漢肺炎 = 90% 死亡率。"},{"pid":"3c15371ed256ba1f9624ddf1b045a374b5530fd7","tid":1882561,"uid":3302,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:42:34.000Z","msg":"支那狗死好"},{"pid":"777a20e16bca3e8c8f572f15b3d4f32cd8b91abd","tid":1882561,"uid":105976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8d382b537584cf6a5f6dec4c83c985f2d806a8af","tid":1882561,"uid":39855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:41:04.000Z","msg":"香港死果個又係有糖尿病，睇嚟 糖尿病 + 武漢肺炎 = 90% 死亡率。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T10:45:39.000Z","msg":"聽講隻病毒除左肺之外仲會攻擊腎"}]}